OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FThe ballot for next year's TCS London
OL,7,FMarathon has opened as this year's
OL,8,Frunners make final preparations for
OL,9,FSunday when warm weather is forecast.
OL,11,FPeople have until 4pm on Friday May 1
OL,12,Fto try their luck in the random draw
OL,13,Ffor next year's event, which will take
OL,14,Fplace on Sunday April 25, with ballot
OL,15,Fresults to be announced by early July.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
