OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777054266
OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FA record-breaking 1,133,813 people
OL,7,Fapplied for a ballot place for
OL,8,FSunday's marathon but the odds of
OL,9,Fgetting lucky may improve for 2027
OL,10,Fwith plans being explored to hold an
OL,11,Fextra London Marathon on Saturday
OL,12,FApril 24.
OL,14,FIf permission is granted for the one-
OL,15,Foff twoday format, all entrants would
OL,16,Fautomatically be entered into the
OL,17,Fballot for both the Saturday and
OL,18,FSunday events, although they would
OL,19,Fonly be able to run in one event.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
