OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FA two-day event would mean more places
OL,7,Ffor charity fundraisers.
OL,9,FJustGiving said #41 million was raised
OL,10,Fon its platform by 2025 participants
OL,11,Fand more than #32 million has already
OL,12,Fbeen donated to more than 14,000
OL,13,Ffundraisers this year.
OL,15,FMarie Curie, the event's charity of
OL,16,Fthe year for 2026, hopes to raise #2
OL,17,Fmillion to fund care for those at the
OL,18,Fend of their lives and support for
OL,19,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
