OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777054266
OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FFor the first time, the London
OL,7,FMarathon weekend gets underway on
OL,8,FFriday evening with a 5k run in
OL,9,FBattersea Park in partnership with
OL,10,FFriday Night Lights which organises
OL,11,Fsocial runs with lights and music.
OL,13,FMarathon runners have until 5.30pm on
OL,14,FSaturday to collect their number from
OL,15,FExcel London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
