PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777054266
OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FAt Excel, people can also sign up to
OL,7,Fgive blood as part of the Blood, Sweat
OL,8,Fand Cheers campaign which is calling
OL,9,Fon the estimated 800,000 spectators at
OL,10,Fthis year's marathon to become donors
OL,11,Fif they are not already.
OL,13,FNHS Blood and Transplant (NHSBT) has
OL,14,Fteamed up with the TCS London Marathon
OL,15,Fand Abbott, which screens more than
OL,16,Fhalf of the world's blood and plasma
OL,17,Fsupply, and 200 Hero medals are
OL,18,Favailable for those who are first to
OL,19,Fcommit to giving blood.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
