FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777054266
OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FEvery minute in England, the NHS uses
OL,7,Fthree life-saving blood donations to
OL,8,Ftreat accident victims, cancer
OL,9,Fpatients, mothers in childbirth and
OL,10,Fpeople living with chronic conditions
OL,11,Flike thalassemia and sickle cell
OL,12,Fdisease.
OL,14,FJust 800,000 active donors are keeping
OL,15,Fthe entire country's blood supply
OL,16,Fgoing and, every year, 200,000 new
OL,17,Fdonors are needed to keep up with
OL,18,Fdemand.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
