PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777054266
OL,3,CBallot for next years London Marathon
OL,4,Cis now open
OL,6,FThere are currently 61,000
OL,7,Fappointments still to be filled during
OL,8,Fthe next six weeks, including 22,000
OL,9,Fin London donor centres.
OL,11,FThe NHS is calling for more donors
OL,12,Fwith B negative, O negative and Ro
OL,13,Fblood types and donors of Black
OL,14,Fheritage to help those living with
OL,15,Fsickle cell disease, the UK's fastest
OL,16,Fgrowing inherited condition, which
OL,17,Fdisproportionately affects people of
OL,18,Fblack heritage.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
